trans-unit.source: IntelliCode saves you time by putting what you're most likely to use at the top of your completion list.
trans-unit.target: IntelliCode saves you time by putting what you're most likely to use at the top of your completion list.

trans-unit.source: IntelliCode recommendations are based on thousands of open source projects on GitHub each with over 100 stars.
trans-unit.target: IntelliCode recommendations are based on thousands of open source projects on GitHub each with over 100 stars.

trans-unit.source: When combined with the context of your code, the completion list is tailored to promote common practices.
trans-unit.target: When combined with the context of your code, the completion list is tailored to promote common practices.

trans-unit.source: IntelliCode isn’t limited to statement completion.
trans-unit.target: IntelliCode isn’t limited to statement completion.

trans-unit.source: Signature help also recommends the most likely overload for your context.
trans-unit.target: Signature help also recommends the most likely overload for your context.

trans-unit.source: AI-assisted recommendations for your own code (Preview)
trans-unit.target: AI-assisted recommendations for your own code (Preview)

trans-unit.source: With this preview feature, if you’re using C#, you can have IntelliCode build a custom model to provide recommendations on code that isn’t in the open source domain, such as methods on your own utility classes or domain specific library calls.
trans-unit.target: With this preview feature, if you’re using C#, you can have IntelliCode build a custom model to provide recommendations on code that isn’t in the open source domain, such as methods on your own utility classes or domain specific library calls.

trans-unit.source: To build your model, we locally extract a summary file from your code and submit it to our service to build your model.
trans-unit.target: To build your model, we locally extract a summary file from your code and submit it to our service to build your model.

trans-unit.source: Our preview service keeps the trained models secured so only you and those you choose to share them with can access them – your model and what it’s learnt about your code stays private to you.
trans-unit.target: Our preview service keeps the trained models secured so only you and those you choose to share them with can access them – your model and what it’s learnt about your code stays private to you.
